author: Kelsey Hendrix
title: Sports Illustrated Swimsuit 2016 Casting Call: Xenia Deli - Swim Daily
text:
by Kelsey Hendrix Posted: Fri Oct. 23, 2015 SI Swimsuit 2016 castings are under way, and as we search for the world's most beautiful women, we invite you to follow along on our journey through the infamous Swim Daily casting call posts. That means when we meet SI Swimsuit hopefuls, so will you!
Next up is Xenia Deli , a gorgeous, New-York based model, who is well-known for her work with VS Pink and Paul Mitchell. And while we're willing to bet you didn't know that Xenia's guilty pleasure is sleeping on the beach, you probably already know those infamous eyebrows and that flawless figure!
Join along as she plays our "Emoji Game " in the video above, and be sure to check out her bio below where she'll reveal the best dish she can cook, her biggest fear, and so much more!
Keep coming back to Swim Daily every Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday and Friday for more 2016 SI Swimsuit Casting Calls !
